'''鹤形目'''（[[學名|學名]]：Gruiformes）在[[生物分类学|生物分类学]]上是[[鸟纲|鸟纲]]中的一个[[目_(生物)|目]]。在2020年的一份研究中認為與[[鴴形目|鴴形目]]（Charadriiformes）親緣相近。<ref name=Kuhletal2020>{{cite journal | first1 = H. | last1 = Kuhl | first2 = C. | last2 = Frankl-Vilches | first3 = A. | last3 = Bakker | first4 = G. | last4 = Mayr | first5 = G. | last5 = Nikolaus | first6 = S. T. | last6 = Boerno | first7 = S. | last7 = Klages | first8 = B. | last8 = Timmermann | first9 = M. | last9 = Gahr | year = 2020 | title = An unbiased molecular approach using 3’UTRs resolves the avian family-level tree of life. | journal = Molecular Biology and Evolution | pages = 143 | doi = 10.1093/molbev/msaa191|pmc=7783168  | doi-access = free }}</ref>
